# How It Works in Your Project

```
Internet
     │
     ▼
Google Cloud Load Balancer
     │
     ▼
Service
e-track-app-svc
     │
     ▼
Deployment
     │
 ┌───┴─────────────┐
 ▼                 ▼
Pod-1          Pod-2
Spring Boot    Spring Boot
```

The Service automatically distributes requests across both application Pods.

---

# Load Balancing

Suppose two replicas are running:

```
Replica 1
Spring Boot

Replica 2
Spring Boot
```

Requests arrive as:

```
Request 1 → Pod 1

Request 2 → Pod 2

Request 3 → Pod 1

Request 4 → Pod 2
```

If Pod 1 crashes:

```
Request
   │
   ▼
LoadBalancer
   │
   ▼
Pod 2
```

Users continue accessing the application without interruption.

